{"tid":2084310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"波頓新書曝：維尼親自跪求川普放了支興、支為一馬","createTime":"2020-06-29T07:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T08:40:56.000Z","uid":32511,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"72d98a48ac83d343bc2da2741161d90d89a7f207","tid":2084310,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200629001203-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200629001203-260408&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=05e36871\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200629001203-260408</a>"},{"pid":"be222dfc709aff0ccc5cbd683cd197c286d9c5f0","tid":2084310,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116b7b152939a70ee702b907c244bab44858d0b3","tid":2084310,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c3e20f5002d6bd3da6519ee630ca7de77b44be","tid":2084310,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"My best friend <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8330f11b8074f230b709e7d90ece9543d4fbaf2","tid":2084310,"uid":28397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:43:20.000Z","msg":"做乜兩個求嚟求去"},{"pid":"a7a1736470725caed6ea0da33bead9bcb896c49f","tid":2084310,"uid":123926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"睇埋佢本書嘅相關新聞先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200625003242-260408?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200625003242-260408%3Fchdtv&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=3eeaa848\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200625003242-260408?chdtv</a><br />\n<br />\n罵聲四起！批波頓新書誤導、操弄 這國也開嗆了<br />\n<br />\n針對波頓新書中的爆料內容，土耳其總統府通訊署署長阿爾通（Fahrettin Altun）昨（24）日在推特上開砲，批評波頓新書「誤導、片面呈現、操弄艾爾段和川普的對話」，稱兩國元首付出很大努力修補兩國關係，稱讚川普比前幾任美國總統付諸更多行動傾聽北約盟友。<br />\n<br />\n波頓新書內容砲火四射，在多國掀起波瀾，不只土耳其，新書中更形容南韓總統文在寅為了面子問題，硬要出席川普與北韓最高領導人金正恩去年6月在板門店的會面，遭青瓦台回擊「扭曲事實」。"},{"pid":"b3b47dc51c2456ab4f12e23cdc297b9fbbaf1feb","tid":2084310,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"中時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d43fccec4010f605b465ca53e913233ec4d115","tid":2084310,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:58:55.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"5af0e8bd058bfc7bdc0c06d837154b17b59cf168","tid":2084310,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"兩條友互「求」  其實阿波生係咪誤會左求既意思"},{"pid":"6a70df5e97d453878c68a016aa777f338a90f2b0","tid":2084310,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:05:59.000Z","msg":"新書中更形容南韓總統文在寅為了面子問題，硬要出席川普與北韓最高領導人金正恩去年6月在板門店的會面，遭青瓦台回擊「扭曲事實」。<br />\n<br />\n毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65284b98d0938f85c13f8ec3dec646c43fecf1af","tid":2084310,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a70df5e97d453878c68a016aa777f338a90f2b0","ti